CODE STRUCTURE for escape fraction
[analysis. : calc_fesc] 
-> [Afesc.c : AextEscapeFraction]
print and pick halos of interest; reduce and print averages
->[Afesc.c : AfeSumOverCells] - >AfeAddOneLocation
->AfeAddOneLocation 
RT ->cdTraverseSky
noRT inplace ->losTraverseSky with a provided worker function 
integrated_pix_lum[ipix] = lum*absorption
Fe (.num, .var_ids)  given by struct AfeInfo Afe_912A declaration in Afesc.c
Afe_912A_abs_ is the "absorption" function used to combine in var_ids in Afesc.c



